{"tid":1039923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［絲入］被老公鬧晒錢","createTime":"2019-02-27T17:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T20:08:25.000Z","uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"da6f48b7f97a5a0c8d06dee0fe55d5728f5f5b5f","tid":1039923,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/28/014015_79ab0a6b9bc58e7f21cd5add3fd6fd59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F28%2F014015_79ab0a6b9bc58e7f21cd5add3fd6fd59.png&h=c58dc5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/28/014017_2b6baef6bfe3ed186b10e8da1426f844.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F28%2F014017_2b6baef6bfe3ed186b10e8da1426f844.png&h=2b394bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSilk'n Silhouette 三源燃脂射頻機<br />\n呢部野半年前買 老公送嘅<br />\n不過今晚先開封 佢幫我一路碌一路話我<br />\n仲話同我賭一百萬肯定無用 話我晒佢錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都有啲懷疑係咪得我咁蠢買<br />\n熱熱地咁 碌完隻手都好攰 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都知做運動好過啦<br />\n但年紀大好難減到 <br />\n想試下家用機<br />\n<br />\n有無絲用過呢部機覺得好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3795ddb889926263e8c25a35482b8a9916683ce","tid":1039923,"uid":42149,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:46:59.000Z","msg":"靠熱就減到肥，呢個世界冇肥人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765e4dbfde52503b1f0e6bf29a5